title: Ep 100: We Made it to 100 Episodes!
description: Holy shit! Episode 100. I've been doing this show for over two years now and what have I learned? This episode lays it all out. Top lessons from doing 100 episodes of That's Deep Bro. Let's get so deep we get our lives!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
